        <p style="text-align: center;"><a name="map02"></a><strong><span style="font-size: 13px;">このおすすめプランのルートをMAPで確認</span></strong></p>
        <p style="text-align: center;"><iframe width="300" height="300" src="https://maps.google.co.jp/maps/ms?msid=206685520380219975254.0004b6a08805063c8fbda&amp;msa=0&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;t=m&amp;brcurrent=3,0x0:0x0,1&amp;source=embed&amp;ll=-27.586198,153.314209&amp;spn=2.920975,3.295898&amp;z=7&amp;output=embed" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe><br />
        <small><a href="https://maps.google.co.jp/maps/ms?msid=206685520380219975254.0004b6a08805063c8fbda&msa=0&ie=UTF8&t=m&brcurrent=3,0x0:0x0,1&source=embed&ll=-27.586198,153.314209&spn=2.920975,3.295898&z=7" style="text-align: center;" onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&amp;PartnerId=google');" target="_blank">大きな地図で見る</a></small></p>
        <br />
        <br />
        <p style="text-align: center;"><img alt="" src="/contentimages/Campaigns/campaigns-jp-erica-plan-page14-hl02.jpg" /></p>
